Xpresstrade chart features

- Automatially-updating charts -- no need to refresh
- Standard bar, line, curve, or candlestick chart types
- 10 different chart horizons ranging from tick to monthly
- Draw and erase multiple trendlines quickly and easily
- Zoom in on particular sections of any chart for closer inspection
- Choose from over 20 technical studies and additional indicators
- Change colors, resize, move, or minimize the chart window
- Save frequently used charts for convenient access
- Price alerts send e-mail notifications when targets are hit
- Jump to an order entry screen via a convenient link
- Print charts quickly and easily 

